 we have encountered many unimaginable situations.

480
00:24:13,340 --> 00:24:16,740
 We all want to go to an ideal place.

481
00:24:16,740 --> 00:24:18,940
 We often say that we don't like the situation.

482
00:24:18,940 --> 00:24:20,540
 We don't like the place.

483
00:24:20,540 --> 00:24:22,740
 We don't like the context.

484
00:24:22,740 --> 00:24:24,540
 So we want to escape.

485
00:24:24,540 --> 00:24:26,940
 We think everything is OK.

486
00:24:26,940 --> 00:24:29,340
 Of course, this is human reason.

487
00:24:29,340 --> 00:24:31,740
 But this story seems to tell us

488
00:24:31,740 --> 00:24:36,340
 what is the most important thing in the eyes of God.

489
00:24:36,340 --> 00:24:38,540
 The most important thing is not what we think.

490
00:24:38,540 --> 00:24:42,340
 Everything is fine.

491
00:24:42,340 --> 00:24:43,940
 In Deuteronomy 14,

492
00:24:43,940 --> 00:24:47,740
 John said, "This is how Jesus saved the Israelites

493
00:24:47,740 --> 00:24:50,340
 from the hands of the Egyptians."

494
00:24:50,340 --> 00:24:54,540
 It says that after crossing the Red Sea,

495
00:24:54,540 --> 00:24:56,540
 what did the Israelites see?

496
00:24:56,540 --> 00:24:58,740
 They saw Jehovah's Witnesses.

497
00:24:58,740 --> 00:25:00,140
 What did the Israelites see?

498
00:25:00,140 --> 00:25:04,340
 They saw the great things that Jehovah did to the Egyptians.

499
00:25:04,340 --> 00:25:06,740
 They knew how to glorify Him.

500
00:25:06,740 --> 00:25:08,540
 They knew how to trust God

501
00:25:08,540 --> 00:25:11,940
 and His divine magic.

502
00:25:11,940 --> 00:25:15,540
 Many times, when we encounter difficulties,

503
00:25:15,540 --> 00:25:21,140
 we think that we are leaving this unideal situation.

504
00:25:21,140 --> 00:25:24,540
 We are looking for an ideal paradise.

505
00:25:24,540 --> 00:25:30,340
 If God really wants to lead us to our ultimate goal,

506
00:25:30,340 --> 00:25:33,540
 where there is no disaster, no trouble, no illness,

507
00:25:33,540 --> 00:25:37,740
 and we can successfully retire and be happy,

508
00:25:37,740 --> 00:25:42,340
 I think God must be our greatest failure.

509
00:25:42,340 --> 00:25:46,940
 And the most successful one should be the Egyptian Pharaoh.

510
00:25:46,940 --> 00:25:48,940
 Because in the Egyptian Empire,

511
00:25:48,940 --> 00:25:50,340
 if you surrender to him,

512
00:25:50,340 --> 00:25:52,940
 you will be safe and secure.

513
00:25:52,940 --> 00:25:55,340
 So you see, leaving Egypt

514
00:25:55,340 --> 00:26:00,340
 does not mean that the Israelites can live in peace for thousands of years.

515
00:26:00,340 --> 00:26:03,740
 In fact, after the Israelites left Egypt

516
00:26:03,740 --> 00:26:07,340
 and crossed the Red Sea and the Sea of ​​Grass,

517
00:26:07,340 --> 00:26:10,540
 there was a trial.

518
00:26:10,540 --> 00:26:14,740
 God's purpose was to prepare us

519
00:26:14,740 --> 00:26:18,340
 to become a group of people who are faithful to His will.

520
00:26:18,340 --> 00:26:21,140
 This is the greatest blessing.

521
00:26:21,140 --> 00:26:24,540
 The greatest blessing is not that we have no disaster, no illness,

522
00:26:24,540 --> 00:26:25,940
 and no epidemic.

523
00:26:25,940 --> 00:26:29,740
 The greatest blessing is that we can become the people of God

524
00:26:29,740 --> 00:26:31,140
 and make a covenant with Him.

525
00:26:31,140 --> 00:26:36,740
 We have the glory to serve God.

526
00:26:36,740 --> 00:26:38,740
 We are now facing different difficulties.

527
00:26:38,740 --> 00:26:42,340
 Whether it is an epidemic or a setback in life,

528
00:26:42,340 --> 00:26:43,940
 we may need to ask

529
00:26:43,940 --> 00:26:47,140
 whether we will still be faithful to God

530
00:26:47,140 --> 00:26:50,340
 after going through these difficulties and setbacks.

531
00:26:50,340 --> 00:26:55,740
 Whether we will still be faithful to God

532
00:26:55,740 --> 00:26:58,740
 or we will be more sincere to God

533
00:26:58,740 --> 00:27:01,340
 after going through God's command.

534
00:27:01,340 --> 00:27:05,140
 Personally, the Church is the same.

535
00:27:05,140 --> 00:27:09,140
 God told us not to waste the difficult path that He has led us on.

536
00:27:09,140 --> 00:27:11,740
 No matter how bad the epidemic is,

537
00:27:11,740 --> 00:27:16,140
 let the Church go through a new trial.

538
00:27:16,140 --> 00:27:18,140
 Let the Church become a Church

539
00:27:18,140 --> 00:27:20,740
 that is more in line with His will.

540
00:27:20,740 --> 00:27:22,540
 Some scholars have a very interesting point.

541
00:27:22,540 --> 00:27:25,940
 They say that the main thing that the God wants to do

542
00:27:25,940 --> 00:27:29,940
 is not to take Israelites out of Egypt.

543
00:27:29,940 --> 00:27:33,740
 It is not to take the Israelites out of Egypt.

544
00:27:33,740 --> 00:27:35,540
 After they left Egypt,

545
00:27:35,540 --> 00:27:39,340
 you will find that their hearts still return to Egypt.

546
00:27:39,340 --> 00:27:41,340
 They always want to return to the Egyptian Empire

547
00:27:41,340 --> 00:27:45,140
 because there is peace and prosperity and prosperity.

548
00:27:45,140 --> 00:27:47,340
 The main thing that the God wants to do

549
00:27:47,340 --> 00:27:49,340
 when they leave Egypt

550
00:27:49,340 --> 00:27:53,740
 is to take Egypt out of the Israelites.

551
00:27:53,740 --> 00:27:57,340
 He wants to take Egypt out of the lives of the Israelites

552
00:27:57,340 --> 00:28:03,740
 as well as the lives of the Pharaohs,

553
00:28:03,740 --> 00:28:07,740
 as well as the lives of the people on earth

554
00:28:07,740 --> 00:28:11,940
 who have no disaster or disease.

555
00:28:11,940 --> 00:28:15,740
 So that we can truly return to God

556
00:28:15,740 --> 00:28:18,540
 and be loyal to Him

557
00:28:18,540 --> 00:28:20,140
 and serve Him

558
00:28:20,140 --> 00:28:23,740
 and be faithful to Him.

559
00:28:23,740 --> 00:28:25,940
 Are we willing to do that?

560
00:28:25,940 --> 00:28:29,340
 Let God take away these idols

561
00:28:29,340 --> 00:28:32,540
 so that our hearts can truly return to Him.

562
00:28:32,540 --> 00:28:36,740
 Let us pray with our hearts.

563
00:28:36,740 --> 00:28:38,740
 God, we know that Your path

564
00:28:38,740 --> 00:28:40,740
 and Your command

565
00:28:40,740 --> 00:28:43,540
 are not what we humans think.

566
00:28:43,540 --> 00:28:45,140
 Your ultimate goal

567
00:28:45,140 --> 00:28:50,140
 is for our lives to return to You.

568
00:28:50,140 --> 00:28:52,740
 Lord, we beg You to take away from our lives

569
00:28:52,740 --> 00:28:57,740
 the things we long for, the so-called peace and prosperity

570
00:28:57,740 --> 00:29:02,340
 so that the country on earth can give us benefits.

571
00:29:02,340 --> 00:29:06,340
 Lord, let our lives truly return to You

572
00:29:06,340 --> 00:29:08,940
 and let You be our true Lord.

573
00:29:08,940 --> 00:29:11,140
 You continue to lead our lives

574
00:29:11,140 --> 00:29:13,740
 and the path ahead of us

575
00:29:13,740 --> 00:29:18,140
 no matter what difficulties we are experiencing.

576
00:29:18,140 --> 00:29:20,740
 Lord, let us know that the ultimate goal

577
00:29:20,740 --> 00:29:24,940
 in Your eyes is not only to have no worries and disasters

578
00:29:24,940 --> 00:29:28,540
 but also that our lives can truly return to You.

579
00:29:28,540 --> 00:29:29,940
 Continue to train us

580
00:29:29,940 --> 00:29:31,940
 and continue to help us and mislead us

581
00:29:31,940 --> 00:29:34,940
 so that we can become more useful

582
00:29:34,940 --> 00:29:38,340
 and more obedient to Your will.

583
00:29:38,340 --> 00:29:39,340
 We pray in this way.

584
00:29:39,340 --> 00:29:40,340
 Amen.

